---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Pricing — Voq"
  description="Voq is free to read pages aloud. Unlimited natural AI voice starts at $2/mo, locked in forever for founding users — no account or sign-up required."
>
<div class="container">
<main class="pricing-page">

  <section class="hero">
    <span class="eyebrow">no logins. no accounts. no nonsense.</span>
    <h1>Voq is free.<br/>Unlimited robot-voice is <em>extra</em>.</h1>
    <p class="sub">
      Read-aloud, on-device voices, highlighting, speed control — all free, forever.
      Want the fancy human-sounding AI voice with no daily limit? That'll cost you
      less than a coffee. A bad coffee. A gas-station coffee.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="tiers">
    <div class="tier">
      <span class="tag">founding rate</span>
      <h2>$2<span>/mo</span></h2>
      <p class="who">First 20 people, ever</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tier">
      <span class="tag">still cheap</span>
      <h2>$3<span>/mo</span></h2>
      <p class="who">Next 20 (spots 21–40)</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tier">
      <span class="tag">reasonable</span>
      <h2>$4<span>/mo</span></h2>
      <p class="who">Next 60 (spots 41–100)</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tier">
      <span class="tag">the "you're late" rate</span>
      <h2>$5<span>/mo</span></h2>
      <p class="who">Everyone after spot 100</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <p class="lockin">
    Whatever price you lock in stays yours <strong>forever</strong> — even if we're
    at $5/mo by the time your friend signs up, your $2 stays $2. Early birds win.
    Actual worms not included.
  </p>

  <section class="whatyoget">
    <h2>Okay but what am I actually paying for?</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>🎧 A voice that doesn't sound like a GPS from 2009</h3>
        <p>The free version uses your browser's built-in voice — fine, functional,
        a little robotic. The paid tier uses proper AI text-to-speech that
        actually sounds like a person, not a Speak & Spell.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>♾️ No more "you've used your free minutes today"</h3>
        <p>Free tier caps out at ~10 minutes of natural voice per day. Paid tier
        gives you a very generous daily budget — enough that you'd have to be
        reading basically nonstop to hit it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>👀 Rest for your eyeballs</h3>
        <p>Long articles, dense docs, that novel you keep meaning to finish —
        let Voq read it while you do literally anything else. Dishes. Walks.
        Staring at a wall. We don't judge.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>💸 You're funding a tiny, honest project</h3>
        <p>No VC money, no ads, no data broker deals. Just a small tool trying
        to cover its own server bills. Your $2–5/mo keeps the lights on and
        keeps Voq weird and independent.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="noaccounts">
    <h2>Wait, there's really no sign-up?</h2>
    <p>
      Correct. No email, no password, no "create an account to continue."
      You pay through Stripe's checkout, you get a short code back, you paste
      it into the Voq panel. That's the whole system.
    </p>
    <p>
      Once you've activated a code in Chrome, it just works — it remembers
      itself automatically, even if you uninstall and reinstall the extension,
      as long as you're signed into the same Chrome profile. Get a new
      computer, or want to move it somewhere else entirely? If your old
      device has been quiet for about a week, the code frees itself up
      automatically so you can activate it again elsewhere. No support ticket,
      no "please verify your identity," no email required — because there was
      never one to begin with.
    </p>
    <p class="tiny">
      (One code = one active device at a time, so it can't be shared across a
      dozen people at once — but moving it to your own next laptop is designed
      to just work.)
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <h2>Ready to upgrade?</h2>
    <p>Open Voq on any page, hit the free daily limit (or just click the key
    icon), and hit upgrade. Two minutes, no account, done.</p>
    <a
      class="install-btn"
      href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ckkihjnakpnccnmdipbdibeaibigjjde"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener"
    >Install Voq — it's free</a>
  </section>

</main>
</div>
</Base>

<style>
  .pricing-page {
    max-width: 880px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 64px 24px 96px;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    color: #0a0a0a;
  }

  .hero { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 56px; }
  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #6b6b6b;
    background: #f4f4f4;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 48px);
    line-height: 1.15;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 18px;
  }
  .hero h1 em { font-style: normal; color: #7c3aed; }
  .hero .sub {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #4b4b4b;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .tiers {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .tier {
    border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px 16px;
    text-align: center;
    background: #fff;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease;
  }
  .tier:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
  .tier .tag {
    display: block;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: #7c3aed;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .tier h2 {
    font-size: 34px;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0 0 6px;
  }
  .tier h2 span { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #999; }
  .tier .who { font-size: 13px; color: #666; margin: 0; }

  .lockin {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #555;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto 72px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .whatyoget { margin-bottom: 72px; }
  .whatyoget h2, .noaccounts h2, .cta h2 {
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 32px;
  }
  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .card {
    background: #fafafa;
    border: 1px solid #ececec;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px;
  }
  .card h3 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 8px; }
  .card p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #555; margin: 0; }

  .noaccounts {
    background: #f8f7ff;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 40px 32px;
    margin-bottom: 72px;
  }
  .noaccounts p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #333;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
  }
  .noaccounts .tiny { font-size: 12.5px; color: #888; text-align: center; }

  .cta { text-align: center; }
  .cta p { font-size: 15px; color: #555; max-width: 460px; margin: 0 auto 24px; }
  .install-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #0a0a0a;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 15px;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.15s ease;
  }
  .install-btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .tiers { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
